products.Title: Vela Blue Stitch Freedom
products.Body:
﻿﻿ABOUT ME

Featuring Vela's Threads Collection! A traditional Middle Eastern scarf used by various countries as well as became a national symbol for Palestine. The kuffiyeh print is a symbol of freedom and peace. Due to the delicate fabrication, some minor snagging may occur on the scarf. 

SIZE & FIT 

75.5" length 32" width 

Model wears: one size fits all

LOOK AFTER ME
